html
  style
    link( href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' )
    :stylus
      @import './node_modules/nib/index'
      light-blue = #61CDE4
      icon-width = 30px
      global-reset()
      body
        background light-blue
        color white
        font-family 'Lato', sans-serif
        padding 0
        margin 0
        line-height 1.4em
        font-smoothing antialiased
      img
        margin auto
        display block
        max-height 50vh
      h1
        font-weight normal
        margin 30px 0
      hr
        background transparent
        border 0
        border-top 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.7)
        width 60%
        margin 20px auto
      .container
        max-width 560px
        padding 0 20px
        margin auto
        text-align center
      svg
        max-width icon-width
        max-height @max-width
        *
          fill white !important
      .cc svg
        max-width icon-width + 30px
      nav a
        margin-right 20px
        cursor pointer
  body
    .container
      img( src='feather.jpg' )
      h1 Jeff Rabinak
      hr
      nav
        a.cc
          include ./cc.svg
        a
          include ./email.svg
        a
          include ./facebook.svg
        a
          include ./twitter.svg
        a
          include ./instagram.svg
      hr
      p Jeff is a writer/direct/editor/podcaster/jerk of all trades living in Brooklyn, NY. Ask to go birding with him. He'll love it.
